      "content": "i get that, but i feel like my deficiency is already pretty bad based on how i feel. i've seen some biohacking forums where people do massive loading doses of 50k or even 100k for a week or two to just reset everything. wouldn't a short burst like that be fine to just jumpstart my levels? it seems like it would be an efficient way to handle the winter slump without waiting weeks for a doctor appointment.",
