      "content": "i'm just really hesitant about the whole doctor thing because i dont want the stress or the cost of all those tests and follow ups. if i were to just stick to a slightly lower but still aggressive amount, like maybe 10,000 or 20,000 iu a day, would that be a much safer middle ground for a quick fix? it feels like a lot more reasonable than 50k, right?",
